    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个阶段。那 Discovery 阶段具体包含哪些步骤？是客户主动找到网站，还是我们推送的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Discovery 阶段主要是客户主动行为：先是 Find website，然后 Browse products。客户满意度分别是 5 分和 4 分，找网站比较容易，但浏览产品会稍微麻烦一点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Find website",
        "Browse products",
        "Customer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Discovery 阶段两个步骤，满意度 5 和 4。那 Purchase 阶段呢？从加购物车开始？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Purchase",
        "Add to cart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Purchase 阶段有三个关键动作：Add to cart、Checkout，最后是 Payment。不过满意度会逐步下降，分别是 3、2、1。支付环节客户体验最差，我们需要重点优化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add to cart",
        "Checkout",
        "Payment",
        "Customer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，标题是 Customer Journey，两个 section 分别是 Discovery 和 Purchase，五个步骤都标了满意度分数。你看一下有没有需要调整的？",
      "elements_involved": [
